# DurationSubtractable - Protocol for types that support subtracting a Duration (- Duration)
module Core

### Defines the protocol `DurationSubtractable`.
protocol DurationSubtractable
  ### Returns the difference between this value and the other value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$sub(you: Duration) -> Me
